===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|車|巠|ls=psc|c1=s|c2=p|t1=carriage}}. The word originally referred to a kind of light carriage.

===Etymology===
STEDT and Schuessler relate this to {{noncog|tbq-pro|*rV-jaŋ|*r-jaːŋ|t=light (weight); lightweight}}, but the initial in the Chinese word is incompatible.

